FILET MIGNON
Charbroiled Tenderloin Steak enhanced by a Madeira
Wine Sauce. With Lyonnaise Potatoes, Green Peas and
Carrot Sticks.
VEAL ESCALOPE A LA CREME
Escalopes of Veal lightly Sauteed in Butter, topped
with a Cream Sauce and Mushrooms. Served with
Fresh Buttered Fettuccine and Spinach Paysanne.
CHICKEN BREAST CHASSEUR
A Boneless Chicken Supreme topped with a
Piquante Sauce of Mushrooms, Tomatoes, White
Wine and Mixed Herbs. Garnished with Pommes
Duchesse and Green Beans.
